# Privacy Policy

**Last updated:** September 1, 2024

## 1. Information Collection

Our app does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. All data entered into the app is stored locally on the user’s device and is not transmitted to any external servers or third-party services.

## 2. Use of Information

Since our app does not collect any data, there is no information used for any purpose outside the functionality of the app. All data remains under the user’s control and is accessible only on the user’s device.

## 3. Data Sharing

We do not share any user information with third parties. All data processed within the app remains strictly on the user’s device.

## 4. Data Security

We take the security of your data seriously. All information stored by the app is kept securely on the user’s device. However, we recommend that users take appropriate security measures on their devices to ensure the safety of their information.

## 5. Children’s Privacy

Our app is designed for users of all ages and does not contain harmful or inappropriate content. As the app does not collect any personal data, it does not require parental consent or special measures to protect underage users.

## 6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or change this Privacy Policy at any time. Users are encouraged to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

## 7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the data security of the app, please contact us at:

Zeddy.dev0@gmail.com
